        <item>
            <title>Zeekr 009 Deluxe 两驱版抵港，内栊豪华舒适 + 空气悬挂可升降 45mm</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/zeekr009-deluxe-hk-launch/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=zeekr009-deluxe-hk-launch</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/zeekr009-deluxe-hk-launch/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 14:15:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MPV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Zeekr]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Zeekr 009]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[极氪]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1297546</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>由锦龙汽车集团代理的高端电动车品牌 Zeekr 在香港正式推出全新 Zeekr 009 Deluxe 双电版本，进一步丰富其在港市场的产品阵容。这款豪华电动 MPV 以「Every Seat Matters」为设计理念，专为家庭及商务用家打造顶级舒适与尖端科技体验。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297586" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155556-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155556-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155556-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Zeekr 009 Deluxe &#8211; Launch Edition 搭载高效双电机系统，提供最大马力 335 hp（250 kW） 及 373 Nm 峰值扭力，从 0-100 km/h 加速仅需 7.9 秒，展现出色动力表现。配备 116 kWh 大容量电池，续航里程达 604 公里（WLTP） 或 740 公里（CLTC），足以应付长途出行需求。此外，支援 150 kW 直流快充，可在短时间内迅速补充电量，兼顾效率与便利。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297585" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155534-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155534-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155534-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297587" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155601-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155601-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_155601-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Zeekr 009 Deluxe 双电版的内饰设计奢华，车厢采用高级物料打造，配备六座独立座椅，每位乘客都能享受宽敞舒适的乘坐体验。第二排座椅更提供电动调节、通风、加热及按摩功能，媲美头等舱享受。车内搭载 15.4 吋中控触控屏幕，及全液晶仪表板，支援智能语音控制及 OTA 在线升级，让驾驶者轻松掌控车辆状态。此外， 009 Deluxe 采用单腔空气悬挂，可升高降低 45mm，实现市场上其中一款最低平台（离地 37.2mm）的豪华 MPV，方便乘客轻松进出车辆。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297588" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160741-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160741-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160741-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297590" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160751-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160751-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160751-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297589" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160744-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160744-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250313_160744-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>科技配置方面，Zeekr 009 配备 L2+ 级智能驾驶辅助系统，包括自适应巡航控制、车道保持辅助及自动泊车功能，大幅提升行车安全与便利性。此外，车辆内置 30 个 YAMAHA 环回立体声高级音响系统、17 吋吸顶屏幕及全景天幕，为乘客带来影音娱乐与开扬空间感。行李空间灵活多变，后排座椅放平后可提供充足储物容量，满足家庭出游或商务运输的多样需求。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/009spev-694x333.png" alt="" width="694" height="333" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/009spev-694x333.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/009spev.png 1050w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>新车定价由 HK$650,000 起，即日起接受预订。想了解 Zeekr 009 更多资料，可到 Zeekr 太古城展示厅（每日 09:00-19:30）或 Zeekr Space 理光中心（每日 09:00-19:00）参观，另有位于新界荃湾的 Zeekr 品牌体验中心（星期一至六 09:00-18:30）提供试驾服务。</p><p>查询热线：2111 1009。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/zeekr009-deluxe-hk-launch/life-tech/auto/">Zeekr 009 Deluxe 两驱版抵港，内栊豪华舒适 + 空气悬挂可升降 45mm</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
