            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1297652</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>就在上星期，笔者才在西班牙巴塞举行的 MWC 大会中，为大家报导过 Samsung 低调现身的两部全新 A 系中阶手机 Galaxy A56 及 Galaxy A36，没想到 Samsung 今日已正式在香港发布，而且亦公布了开售详情，现在就让 Edward 带大家到现场睇睇啦。</p><h2>双 A 颜色抢眼仍针对年青族群</h2><p>对 Samsung 手机有一定认知的读者，应该都会知道 A 系是属于中阶机款，而且一向主打年青用家族群，去到今代的 Galaxy A56 及 A36 亦不例外。今次两部 A 系新机，机背均采用了强化玻璃配以鲜艳颜色作设计，当中较入门的 Galaxy A36 设有两个规格：8 + 128GB 版本设有亮夜黑及亮薰紫两只颜色，而 8 + 256GB 版本就除了这两只颜色外，更设有亮冰白及亮青绿两只颜色。至于较高阶的 Galaxy A56 就只设 12 + 256GB 一个规格，设有雾炭灰、雾墨绿、雾浅灰及雾樱粉 4 只颜色选择，颜色均走清新鲜艳抢眼路线，应该会颇受年青人欢迎。而在设计上，Galaxy A36 及 A56 其实差不多，两者均内建了 6.7 吋 Super AMOLED 荧幕及三主镜设计，最能将两机分辨出来的只有机边：A36 采用净色设计，而 A56 就加入了拉丝纹理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297666" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_135638-694x523.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="523" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_135638-694x523.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_135638.jpg 1195w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297668" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_135645-694x523.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="523" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_135645-694x523.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_135645.jpg 1195w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次 Samsung 推出的全新 Galaxy A 系中阶机：Galaxy A36（第一张）及 Galaxy A56（第二张），均采用了鲜艳抢眼的配色，针对年青用家族群。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297669" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140758-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140758-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140758.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297670" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141105-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141105-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141105.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲无论是 Galaxy A36（第一张）还是 Galaxy A56（第二张），机背依然采用了强化玻璃物料制造。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297672" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140808-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140808-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140808.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297673" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141055-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141055-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141055.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy A36（第一张）及 A56（第二张），同样在机身右侧设有开关键及音量键，亦同样采用了二段式设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297674" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140814-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140814-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140814.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297675" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141050-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141050-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141050.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy A36 及 A56 其实在机身设计上十分相似，最易分辨两者的地方，就是机侧：A36 采用纯银色设计（第一张）而 A56 就加入了拉丝纹理（第二张）。</p><h2>两机同采三主镜设计配置有异成像合理</h2><p>至于相机方面，Samsung Galaxy A36 及 A56 均内建了 3 个主镜头设计，而且今代并非再采用三个独立镜头组，而是使用了一个黑玻璃片保护三个镜头，令设计上终于与上代有少许分别。至于镜头配置方面，两机同样采用了主摄镜 + 超广角镜 + 微距镜的配置，不过像素上就有分别：Galaxy A36 的主摄镜、超广角镜及微距镜像素分别为 5,000 万、800 万及 500 万，而 Galaxy A56 的主摄镜、超广角镜及微距镜像素则分别为 5,000 万、1,200 万及 500 万。而两机前镜均同样采开孔式设计，像素亦同样为 1,200 万。至于成像方面，老实说作为中阶机，笔者对它们的期望不算很大，不过出来的效果依然算不俗，虽然以人像模式拍摄虚化效果会有少许「假」，但整体来说仍算不错，唯一是它们毕竟未有内建长焦镜，所以拍摄远物时不但不能拍得很远，清晰度亦不太理想。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297676" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140852-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140852-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_140852.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297677" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141112-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141112-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250314_141112.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲镜头方面，A36（第一张）及 A56（第二张）均采用了 3 主镜设计，两机同样内建了 5,000 万像素主摄镜及 500 万像素微距镜，唯一是超广角镜，A36 只支援至 800 万像素，而 A56 就支援至 1,200 万。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297679" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143541-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143541-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143541-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297680" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143545-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143545-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143545-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297681" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143548-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143548-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143548-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143553-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143553-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143553-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲先来看 Galaxy A36 镜头表示，笔者在日间室外分别以超广角镜（第一张）、主摄镜 1x（第二张）、主摄镜 2x（第三张）及主摄镜 4x（第四张）拍摄，大家可以见到成像不算十分有惊喜，但总算清晰度高，颜色还原度亦不错。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297684" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143457-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143457-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143457-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297685" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143459-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143459-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143459-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297686" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143501-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143501-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143501-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297687" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143504-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143504-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143504-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于 Galaxy A56 的成像方面，笔者以相同焦距试拍，结果觉得它们与 A36 的成像效果差不多，不过观感上以 Galaxy A56 拍摄似乎清晰度更高一点，相片的立体感亦较佳。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297683" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143556-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143556-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143556-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297688" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143507-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143507-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143507-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不过始终两机均未设长焦镜配置，所以使用主摄镜配合数码变焦拍摄远物，无论是 Galaxy A36（第一张）还是 A56（第二张）其实也只属一般。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297689" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143419-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143419-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143419-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297690" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143443-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143443-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143443-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于微距镜方面，无论是使用 Galaxy A36（第一张）还是 A56（第二张）拍摄，效果也算不错，当中 A56 的成像似乎更好一点。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297691" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143816-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143816-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143816-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297692" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143804-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143804-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143804-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于在室内拍摄物件，笔者也觉得 Galaxy A56（第二张）出来的效果会比 A36（第一张）好，但差距不算远。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1297694 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143353-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143353-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143353-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1297695 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143324-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143324-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143324-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于人像拍摄方面，笔者也觉得 Galaxy A56（右）出来的效果比较理想，A36（左）拍出来感觉会较青，色准不算好。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1297696 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143633-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143633-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143633-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1297697 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143707-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143707-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_143707-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于前镜效果方面，同样是 Galaxy A56（右）出来的效果会比 A36（左）来得自然及理想。</p><br /><b>
]]>
